Incident Summary:
On the night of 5th February 2025, an electrical short-circuit in the kitchen led to a small fire, resulting in smoke damage to walls and partial damage to appliances. The fire was controlled within 20 minutes. No injuries were reported. Fire services report: FSR-2025-8872.

Damaged Items:
- Microwave Oven (Severely Damaged)
- Kitchen Cabinets (Partially Burned)
- Refrigerator (Smoke Damage)
- Electrical Wiring (Affected Section)

